1. *On* je bio povređen u nesreći. (He was injured in an accident.)
2. Ona je bila *povređena* od uragana. (She was injured by the hurricane.)
3. *Povređenom* se treba pomoći. (Help should be given to the injured one.)
4. *Povređivanje* nije dopušteno. (Injuring is not allowed.)
5. *Povređivač* je morao da snosi posledice. (The injurer had to bear the consequences.)